### ── RESERVATION SERVICE (/reservation) ────────────────────────────────────
### Ortam: Ctrl+Shift+P → Rest Client: Switch Environment → dev
### NOT: createReservation sonrası dönen reservationId'yi sonraki isteklerde kullan.

### 1. Rezervasyon oluştur — Customer Bauer, Tesla Model 3 (BER)
# @name createRes
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservation/createReservation
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000016",
  "notes": "Bitte bis Freitag reservieren"
}

### 2. Rezervasyonları listele — Admin (tüm şubeler)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservation/Reservations
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 3. Rezervasyonları listele — Customer Bauer (sadece kendi rezervasyonları)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservation/Reservations
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 4. Rezervasyonu onayla — Operator
### reservationId: 1. adımdan dönen ID'yi buraya yaz
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservation/approveReservation
Authorization: {{operatorAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservationId": "BURAYA_ID_YAZ"
}

### 5. Aynı araca çift rezervasyon — reddedilmeli (araç zaten RESERVED)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservation/createReservation
Authorization: {{customerHoffmannAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000016",
  "notes": "Doppelbuchung-Test"
}

### 6. Rezervasyonu iptal et — Customer Bauer
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservation/cancelReservation
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservationId": "BURAYA_ID_YAZ"
}

### 7. İptal edilen araç tekrar rezerve edilebilmeli
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservation/createReservation
Authorization: {{customerHoffmannAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000016",
  "notes": "Jetzt wieder frei"
}
